{{!
  PROFILE CUSTOM TABS SNIPPET

  Adds the "Inklings" tab to the character profile page tab list.

  FILE: ares-webportal/app/components/profile-custom-tabs.hbs

  STEP 1: Locate the file
  1. Open your game's ares-webportal/app/components/profile-custom-tabs.hbs

  STEP 2: Find the insertion point
  2. Find the <ul> element that contains the profile tab links
  3. Look for the closing </ul> tag
  4. The new <li> should go INSIDE the <ul>, right before the </ul>

  STEP 3: Copy and paste
  5. Copy the <li> block below (between the markers)
  6. Paste it inside the <ul> at the end (before </ul>)
  7. Save the file

  IMPORTANT: DO NOT change the href="#inklings-tab-pane"
  It must match the id="inklings-tab-pane" in profile-custom.snippet.hbs
}}

{{! ---START COPY HERE--- }}
<li class="nav-item">
  <a class="nav-link" data-toggle="tab" href="#inklings-tab-pane">Inklings</a>
</li>
{{! ---END COPY--- }}
